BT /F1 8 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 807.89 Tm (Fulbito Prode 2.0 architecture summary) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 779.89 Tm (20\) Security and Reliability Notes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 760.89 Tm (- Production fails fast when SESSION_SECRET is missing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 747.29 Tm (- Session cookie is HTTP only and secure in production mode.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 733.69 Tm (- Route handlers consistently reject unauthorized requests with 401/403.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 720.09 Tm (- Soft delete strategy for groups and memberships preserves rule compatibility in constrained) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 706.49 Tm (  PocketBase setups.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 692.89 Tm (- Provider health endpoint access is restricted and cached to limit expensive upstream) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 679.29 Tm (  probing.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 657.69 Tm (21\) Known Tradeoffs and Improvement Opportunities) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 638.69 Tm (- Current rate limiting is in process memory; horizontal scale needs shared/edge limiter.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 625.09 Tm (- Session payload currently contains provider token in signed cookie payload; consider token) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 611.49 Tm (  indirection store for stronger separation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 597.89 Tm (- UI state and API route payload mappings are rich but large; additional domain modules could) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 584.29 Tm (  reduce component size.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 570.69 Tm (- Additional observability hooks \(structured logs, tracing IDs, external error tracking\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 557.09 Tm (  would improve incident response.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 543.49 Tm (- Some design artifacts \(UI.jsx and .pen files\) are useful references but not part of runtime) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.2 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 529.89 Tm (  build path.) Tj ET
